{"id":670,"date":"2024-08-02T20:06:44","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T20:06:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=670"},"modified":"2024-08-02T20:06:44","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T20:06:44","slug":"tm041-torment","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm041-torment\/","title":{"rendered":"TM041 Torment"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM041 Torment<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in the Shadow Base B2F, behind a door requiring a level 3 Key Card.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>It enrages the foe, making it incapable of performing the same move successfully.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>15<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Dark<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Defeat Shadow Boss Zeff at the Shadow Base<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to your house at Frozen Heights and head West.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-players-house-at-frozen-heights.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the player\u2019s house at Frozen Heights. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the player\u2019s house at Frozen Heights.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly come across a frozen lake \u2013 walk onto the lake and follow it North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-following-the-frozen-lake-north.jpg\" alt=\"Following the frozen lake North. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the frozen lake North.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll soon see the Shadow Base entrance you want to go through in the lake\u2019s northwest corner.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-shadow-base.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the Shadow Base. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the Shadow Base.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head East directly after entering the base.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-going-east.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path going East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path going East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go through the broken door and head North to enter the elevator.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-elevator.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the elevator. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the elevator.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Speak with the Team Shadow member and have her take you to the base\u2019s B2F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-going-to-the-bases-b2f.jpg\" alt=\"Going to the base\u2019s B2F. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going to the base\u2019s B2F.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Exit the elevator onto B2F and walk South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-exiting-the-elevator-and-walking-south.jpg\" alt=\"Exiting the elevator and walking South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Exiting the elevator and walking South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you can, take the path East where you\u2019ll see the TM for Torment locked behind a door requiring a level 3 Key Card.<\/p>\n<p>Since acquiring the Key Card is mandatory during the mainline quest where the player raids the base, you can easily open the door and take the TM.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-torment-behind-a-locked-door.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Torment behind a locked door. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Torment behind a locked door.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":671,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-670","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/670","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/671"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=670"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=670"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}